subject: Skiing
World Cup (Skiing)
Ski Jumping
Luge Racing
lead_paragraph: Anna Fenninger had a strong finish to capture the World Cup giant slalom in Maribor, Slovenia, and is 84 points behind Tina Maze, the overall leader, with 12 races to go.
